name: Voushart
description:
Voushart  This game is made for  G.W.C.A Game Jam #2 3 day long game jam. GAME IS AVAILABLE FOR WINDOWS screenshots
Lore wise game has you crash on planet  Z-1 04 This planet has oxygen but not enough to run or do other intense activities.Only thing you have left is your space suit that can blend in environment.
